gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 129, Nets 125
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Giannis Antetokounmpos 36 points and 12 rebounds, the Bucks defeated the Nets, 129-125. Damian Lillard added 21 points, six rebounds, and seven assists for the Bucks in the victory, while Cam Thomas led all scorers with 45 points for the Nets in the losing effort. The Bucks improve to 4-2 on the season, while the Nets fall to 3-4.
